solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public int titleToNumber(String s) {--newline--        int result = 0;--newline--        for(int i = 0 ; i < s.length(); i++) {--newline--          result = result * 26 + (s.charAt(i) - 'A' + 1);--newline--        }--newline--        return result;--newline--      }--newline--}
